GnomeSort is a place.
Destination is a place.

The Passenger is a woman.
Sorting is a technique.

[Passenger walks to GnomeSort]
[Passenger asks GnomeSort about [5 2 8 1 9 3]]
[Passenger has i = 0, arr = [5 2 8 1 9 3]]

[While i < length of arr]
[If i is 0]
[i becomes i + 1]
[Else]
[If arr[i] < arr[i - 1]]
[temp = arr[i]]
[arr[i] = arr[i - 1]]
[arr[i - 1] = temp]
[i becomes i - 1]
[Else]
[i becomes i + 1]

[Passenger tells GnomeSort: arr]
